race.comment: Good little contest to start the day. BLUE EYED BRIGID (8) back for her second campaign when stalked the speed at her second run in for a slick maiden win over 1500m at Hawkesbury. Maps well from the draw and has further upside. SANTATIME (2) consistent gelding ready to hit his top third-up. Will relish the mile after closing strongly when third over 1350m at Beaumont (Newcastle). Can sit off them from the draw and close late. OCEAN CHILL (5) Ocean Park mare who went forward on debut with a tough maiden victory over 1400m at Scone. Back in trip when a battling fourth over 1350m at Beaumont (Newcastle). Will appreciate this trip and figure prominently. ROSE WATER (6) is a well-bred mare who stretches in trip third-up. Speared across from the wide draw when a tenacious second over 1350m at Beaumont (Newcastle). Will push forward again at the each-way price.
